# Pinned external sources. Verified by 00-preflight.sh::verify_pins before
# every install — if a SHA goes 404 (rebased / repo deleted) the installer
# aborts loudly rather than silently fetching mismatched code later.
#
# Format: NAME=SHA[#optional comment]
# Repo URLs live in installer/PINS.repos so the same repo can be pinned to
# different shas across NAMEs (e.g. SUPERPOWERS_CORE_SHA + SUPERPOWERS_FORK_SHA).
#
# Comments and blank lines are ignored.

